# Project 2 — TechNova HR Workforce Analytics

## Overview
HR analytics dashboard analyzing 1,470 employee 
attrition patterns across departments, age groups, 
salary bands and gender.

## Key Insights
- Sales dept highest attrition (20.63%) ⚠️
- Young employees (18-25) → 35.77% attrition 🔴
- Low salary = 5x higher attrition than Premium
- Overtime employees → 3x more likely to leave

## Skills Used
COUNTIFS · AVERAGEIFS · MAXIFS · MINIFS · CHOOSE
Conditional Formatting · PivotTables · Dashboard Design
